menu_buildjob_animaltrap
[TITLE]The Manual: Animal Trap Menu[/TITLE]
[B][B]
[C:7:0:1]How to Get Here[C:7:0:0]
[B]
Press [IKEY:D_BUILDJOB] from the main view and move to an animal trap.
[B][B]
[C:7:0:1]Description[C:7:0:0]
[B]
Animal traps catch small animals.  In order for them to be effective, bait must be used.  The type of bait determines the possible captive.
Do not use gems.
[B]
Captured animals can be used for food, extracts or trade. Some can be tamed.
